author: phylsix
body:
We propose a double L2Muon trigger path triggering on displaced muons. JIRA ticket can be found here: 
https://its.cern.ch/jira/browse/CMSHLT-1727

As part of the requirements to be accepted, we add DQM plots for 2 signal paths.
title: add DQM for L2DoubleMuon trigger path.
